Instructors

Higher Education Instructors
Don't know who your local Wiley representative is? Find out using the Who's My Rep page, including phone and email address.
Find the right title for your college course. Browse wiley.com for innovative books, supplements, resources and more.
High School Teachers
For more information about Wiley learning solutions and instructional materials for your high school class, please visit www.wiley.com/go/highschool or contact the Wiley High School Solutions team via email at WileyHSAP@wiley.com or via telephone at 1-855-827-4630.
Jossey-Bass Faculty Development Resources
Are you looking for more ways to be more effective in the classroom? Visit the Jossey-Bass Higher & Adult Education Web site for a wide selection of resources on teaching and learning.
Wiley Learning Institute Online professional development for higher education faculty and campus leaders. Join peers, Jossey-Bass authors, and thought leaders from around the world for interactive workshops on a variety of teaching and learning, discipline specific, and leadership development topics. Learn more at www.WileyLearningInstitute.com.









