US Businesses, Corporations, Government Agencies

Contact Wiley US Corporate & Government Sales Reach your US Corporate or Government sales representative, request bulk direct order discount pricing.


Booksellers

 
Visit the Wiley Bookseller Services Website for additional information.



Wiley Customer Care

(USA, the Americas, & the Caribbean)
Request Pricing, Order Inquiries, & Product Questions Request product pricing, inquire about the status of your order, or obtain information about a product.
Credit Application & Payment InquiriesA completed Credit Application, PDF (75 KB), is required for all Customers seeking a credit line for purchases in excess of $20,000. Contact your Credit Representative to request open billing or payment information on your account.
Journal Customer Services Please contact Journal Customer Services at Wiley for assistance with your journal account.

Get Technical Support for Multimedia Products Get product support for CD-ROMs, e-books, and other multimedia products.
Submit Website Feedback Contact our web team for problems with online ordering, to report a bug, or to make suggestions about this Website.
Request Permission Follow our detailed guidelines for requesting permission to use material from one of our titles.
Questions about Link Exchanges Guidelines on how to join our Affiliate Program.
DMCA Notification If you believe your copyright-protected work was posted on a Wiley site without authorization , please view our DMCA Notification Policy.
 

 









