Company Summary
Wiley John & Sons Inc. is a global publisher of print and electronic products, specializing in scientific, technical, and medical books and journals; professional and consumer books and subscription services; and textbooks and other educational materials for undergraduate and graduate students as well as lifelong learners.  The company has publishing, marketing and distribution centers in the United States, Canada, Europe, Asia, and Australia.   





 



































